    ↓
RawImage.read() → RawImage object {data, width, height, channels}
    ↓
prepareImages() → RawImage[] array
    ↓
this.processor(preparedImages) → {pixel_values, ...other_outputs}
    ↓
pass pixel_values to model or model.generate()
```

**processor() returns object with pixel_values:**
