- **Main pipelines**: `/src/pipelines.js` (lines 1975-2779 for multimodal examples)
- **Image utilities**: `/src/utils/image.js`
- **Test examples**: `/tests/pipelines/test_pipelines_image_to_text.js`, `/tests/pipelines/test_pipelines_zero_shot_image_classification.js`, `/tests/pipelines/test_pipelines_document_question_answering.js`
- **Processor definitions**: `/src/models/processors.js`, `/src/models/image_processors.js`

